---

The test is specifically named for “suffix” expressions and issue #101. The suspicious area is the parser/codegen for suffix expressions (`c.l[0..1]`, `c.l[t_i]`) and temporary register handling. I’ll inspect those source regions and run under gdb with breakpoints there to see generated expression state.

